label: A2B3_mC20_9_2a_3a-001
title: Room Temperature Ga$_{2}$Se$_{3}$ Structure
comments:
Above 645-694K (Villars, 2018) this structure transforms to the \href{current_web_home_dir/AB_cF8_216_a_c-001}{cubic zincblende ($B3$) phase}, with vacancies on the gallium sites to adjust the symmetry (L\"{u}bbers, 1982). 
 (Gh\'{e}mard, 1983) give this structure in the ``unique axis-$c$'' setting of space group \#9.  We used FINDSYM to transform this to the standard ``unique axis-$b$'' setting.
